<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<title></title>
		<style type="text/css">
			.box{
				width: 50px;
				height: 50px;
				background: red;
				margin: 10px;
				border:solid 2px black;
				padding: 20px;
				display: inline;
			}
			span{
				background: blue;
				width: 100px;
				height: 50px;
				display: inline-block;
				border: solid 10px gold;
				padding: 20px;
				margin: 40px;/*上下不起作用*/
			}
			input{
				width: 150px;
				height: 40px;
				padding: 20px;
				margin: 30px;
				display: none;/*隐藏*/
				border: solid 1px black;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h3>1.块状元素,从上往下排列，还可以定义宽高。</h3>
		<div class="box">1</div>
		<div class="box">2</div>
		<h3>2.内联元素,呈一行排列，不可以定义宽高。</h3>
		<span>呵呵</span>
		<span>呵呵</span>
		<h3>3.行内块元素（img，input），呈一行排列，可以定义宽高。</h3>
		<input type="text" />
		<input type="text" />
	</body>
</html>
